</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/Very_low_frequency" title="Very low frequency">VLF</a></td>
<td>Very Low Frequency</td>
<td>3–30 <a href="/wiki/Kilohertz" title="Kilohertz" class="mw-redirect">kHz</a></td>
<td>100–10 km</td>
<td>Guided between the earth and the <a href="/wiki/Ionosphere" title="Ionosphere">ionosphere</a>.</td>
</tr>
